Definition: a rude expression intended to offend or hurt
Example: when a student made a stupid mistake he spared them no abuse; they yelled insults at the visiting team
Synonyms: verb, communication, insult, revilement, revile, contumely, adj, all, disrespectful, contumelious, vilification, vilify, disrespect, a, rude, expression, intended, to, offend, or, hurt, when, student, made, stupid, mistake, he, spared, them, no, they, yelled, insults, at, the, visiting, team
Category: noun.communication
